# ğŸ§  architecture.mmd  
(**Mermaid Architecture Diagram**)

```mermaid
flowchart TD

User -->|Image| OCR[OCR Engine]
User -->|Audio| ASR[Speech-to-Text]
User -->|Text| TextInput[Text Input]

OCR --> Parser
ASR --> Parser
TextInput --> Parser

Parser -->|Structured Problem| Router[Intent Router Agent]

Router --> Solver[Solver Agent]
Solver --> RAG[RAG Retriever]
RAG --> Solver

Solver --> Verifier[Verifier Agent]
Verifier -->|Low Confidence| HITL[Human-in-the-Loop]

Verifier --> Explainer[Explainer Agent]
Explainer --> UI[Streamlit UI]

HITL --> Memory[Memory Store]
Explainer --> Memory

Memory --> Solver
Memory --> Parser
